From 249fb9b43223245e9ded4432681a8dccc126bb01 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Robin Nagpal <robin.nagpal@newsela.com>
Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 14:40:15 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Add Yarn PnP support

Ports the Yarn Plug'n'Play resolution support from upstream PR
microsoft/typescript-go#1966 (author: GGomez99 / guyllian.gomez), adapted
to apply on top of the tsgolint shim patches (keeps the exported
SnapshotFSBuilder / ConfigFileRegistryBuilder names from the shim patch and
threads the new pnpApi through them).

Adds internal/pnp (manifest parser + PnP API) and internal/vfs/pnpvfs, and
wires PnpApi() into the resolver, compiler host and project hosts so module
and tsconfig-extends resolution work inside a Yarn PnP workspace.

Test files, baselines and the VS Code extension change from the PR are
omitted (not needed to build/run tsgolint).
